AGRICULTURE CODE

writing, verbally, or through any form of advertising literature; or
(5) the registrant has not complied or the pesticide does
not comply with a requirement of this chapter or a rule adopted under
this chapter.
Acts 1981, 67th Leg., p. 1194, ch. 388, Sec. 1, eff. Sept. 1, 1981.
Amended by Acts 1995, 74th Leg., ch. 419, Sec. 3.13, eff. Sept. 1,
